Description_lang: Completing quests, opening treasures, and defeating rare enemies in the Maw will now incur the |cFFFF0000Eye of the Jailer|r, who will torment you with punishments of increasing deadliness.

description_blz.en_US: Completing quests, opening treasures, and defeating rare enemies in the Maw will now incur the Eye of the Jailer, who will torment you with punishments of increasing deadliness.
description_blz.es_MX: Completar misiones, abrir tesoros y vencer enemigos raros en las Fauces ahora provoca el Ojo del Carcelero, que te atormentará con castigos cada vez más mortíferos.
description_blz.pt_BR: Completar missões, abrir tesouros e derrotar inimigos raros na Gorja agora atrairá o Olho do Carcereiro, que atormentará você com castigos cada vez mais letais.
description_blz.de_DE: Im Schlund Quests abzuschließen, Schätze zu öffnen oder seltene Gegner zu töten, zieht jetzt das Auge des Kerkermeisters auf Euch. Dieser wird Euch mit zunehmend tödlicheren Strafen quälen.
description_blz.en_GB: Completing quests, opening treasures, and defeating rare enemies in the Maw will now incur the Eye of the Jailer, who will torment you with punishments of increasing deadliness.
description_blz.es_ES: Ahora, al completar misiones, abrir tesoros y derrotar a enemigos poco comunes en Las Fauces atraerás la Mirada del Carcelero, que te atormentará con castigos cada vez más letales.
description_blz.fr_FR: Accomplir des quêtes, ouvrir des trésors et vaincre des ennemis rares dans l’Antre alerte désormais l’œil du Geôlier, qui vous inflige maints châtiments de plus en plus meurtriers.
description_blz.it_IT: Completare le missioni, aprire i tesori e sconfiggere i nemici rari nella Fauce attiva l'Occhio del Carceriere, che tormenta con punizioni di crescente letalità.
description_blz.ru_RU: Выполняя задания, получая сокровища и побеждая редких противников, вы навлекаете на себя взор Ока Тюремщика. Берегитесь, Тюремщик будет насылать на вас все более страшные и смертоносные кары!
description_blz.ko_KR: 나락에서 퀘스트를 완료하거나, 보물 상자를 열거나, 희귀한 적을 처치하면 간수의 눈이 발동하여 점점 치명적으로 변모하는 형벌이 당신을 괴롭힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 在淵喉內完成任務、開啟寶箱和擊敗稀有敵人時，現在都會引來獄主之眼的注視，並對你降下越來越致命的懲罰。
description_blz.zh_CN: 在噬渊完成任务、开启宝箱和击败稀有敌人将会引发典狱长之眼，它将以越来越致命的惩罚折磨你。
